metadata.name: "Bruises" Music Video Game - Scene 2
metadata.description:
It’s almost time to launch the “Bruises” Music Video Game!
    
Welcome to the bedroom - you’re halfway there. This is scene 2 of 4 to claim to get an allowlist spot into the Listening Room. Be sure to also follow Nvak Collective & Annika Rose on Lens for a chance to win a “Bruises” music NFT!

For full details, see Nvak Collective's post on Mirror: https://mirror.xyz/0xf0a11CB9C4771b8F8444B15aD0Fa1109AC6bD209/lhpFmKE1kKLljPIjM8z6ls4BsE5OCoijR_hvgbRrP5k
